title: Shining Through (1992)
description:
Cast:
Michael Douglas
Melanie Griffith
Liam Neeson


Plot:
This World War II drama concerns a love affair between a spy (Michael Douglas) and a secretary (Melanie Griffith) that goes south when duty turns him cold and pushes her into dangerous, behind-the-lines intelligence work. Liam Neeson plays the gentleman Nazi unwittingly providing Griffith with cover as domestic help.
